extends layout
//link(rel="stylesheet", href="/stylesheets/about.css")//
block content
  .about-container
    .about-hero-section
      h1 About Us
      p Welcome to our restaurant, where passion meets flavor! Our culinary journey began with a simple idea: to create a haven for food lovers to savor the finest meals in an inviting and warm atmosphere.
    
    .mission-section
      h2 Our Mission
      p We take pride in sourcing the freshest ingredients and crafting every dish with care. Our mission is to deliver an unforgettable dining experience, whether you are here for a casual meal, a special occasion, or simply to satisfy your cravings.
    
    .chefs-section
      h2 Meet Our Chefs
      p Our talented chefs bring creativity and expertise to every plate, blending traditional techniques with modern flavors to create culinary masterpieces. Come and explore our rich menu and discover why we are the talk of the town.
      .chefs-grid
        .chef-card
          img(src="/images/chef.jpg", alt="Chef Alex")
          h3 Chef Alex
          p With over 15 years of experience, Chef Alex is passionate about crafting dishes that delight the senses.
        .chef-card
          img(src="/images/lady_chef.jpg", alt="Chef Maria")
          h3 Chef Maria
          p Chef Maria specializes in desserts, turning sweet dreams into reality with her exquisite creations.

    .testimonials-section
      h2 What Our Customers Say
      .testimonial
        p "The food is outstanding! Every dish is a work of art." - Sarah
      .testimonial
        p "An amazing dining experience! The atmosphere is perfect." - John

    .call-to-action
      h2 Join Us Today!
      p Your satisfaction is our top priority, and we strive to exceed your expectations with every plate served. We invite you to come and experience the warmth of our hospitality.
      a.btn.btn-primary(href="/menu") View Our Menu
